fea: combat scene
    * enemy selected strategy info
    * attack animation (mb projectile effect)
    * hit taken animation (scale + recolor effect)
    * death animation (scale to 0 + rotate? effect)

    click strategy -> hide btns -> show hero animation -> show enemy animation + strategy name -> show btns
    enemy == hero (character)
    hero parameters: player params
    enemy parameters: custom params instance

    Strategy { id: str }
    Attack { target: Entity, callback: Entity }
    AttackCallback {}
